      <h1 class='title'>Food Labelling</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 cc1753-4WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1753ws' title='Col. 1753WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1753WS' name='column_1753ws' href='#column_1753ws' rel='bookmark'>1753WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_576'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-norman-baker' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_576' title='Link to this speech by Mr Norman Baker' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-norman-baker" title="Mr Norman Baker">Norman Baker</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Health if he will ask the Food Standards Agency to publish good practice guidelines for the use of the term, suitable for vegetarians, on food labels and menus. [188055]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_577'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/miss-melanie-johnson' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_577' title='Link to this speech by Miss Melanie Johnson' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/miss-melanie-johnson" title="Miss Melanie Johnson">Miss Melanie Johnson</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">I refer the hon. Member to the reply I gave to the hon. Member for Portsmouth, South (Mr. Hancock) on <a href="/written_answers/2004/sep/15/ectopic-pregnancies#column_1643w">15 September 2004,<span class="italic">Official Report,</span> columns 1643&#x2013;44W</a>.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_578'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-norman-baker' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_578' title='Link to this speech by Mr Norman Baker' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-norman-baker" title="Mr Norman Baker">Norman Baker</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Health what steps he intends to take to prevent the inclusion in foods labelled as vegetarian of processing agents derived from animals. [188056]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_579'>  </a>
